quote.summary: CaoCao Inc is an investment holding company principally engaged in operating its new energy-focused online ride hailing platform that provides a range of mobility services and other services, as well as selling vehicles. The Company operates four businesses including Mobility Services, Vehicle Leasing, Vehicle Sales, and Other Services. The Company provides mobility services, which covers online ride hailing services under the brands CaoCao Mobility and Limao Mobility, offering express and mobility services. The Company also provides vehicle leasing, offering car rental services to third parties. The Company provides vehicles sales, mainly selling new vehicles, which were purchased from related parties to its car partners, individual drivers, other third-party taxi companies and automobile dealers. Other services include advertising, transportation support services, intra-city delivery service, customer referring service, technological support, and other services.
